The AmbientZone type is used to assign ambient sounds to an area.

It uses two main bounding volumes; an activation volume and a playback volume. The volumes can be defined as spheres, boxes or lines. The position, size and rotation of the two volumes can be defined independently.

AmbientZones use AmbientRules to play sounds. An AmbientZone can use multiple AmbientRules which will play according to their individual settings.

Fields:

Name - metahash - Name of the AmbientRule
Flags - Flags value - Unknown
Flags2 - Flags value - Unknown
Flags3 - Flags value - Unknown
Position - Vector3 value - Offset of the sound relative to the AmbientZone center.
Flags3 - Flags value - Unknown
Hash1 - metahash - Master sound
Hash2 - metahash - Category
Flags4 - Flags value - Unknown
Flags5 - Flags value - Unknown
Flags6 - Flags value - Unknown
Unk01 - Float value - Unknown
InnerRad - Float value - Inner radius of sound - minimum distance the sound can be heard from.
OuterRad - Float value - Outer radius of sound - maximum distance the sound can be heard from.
StartTime - Integer value - Start time, in minutes, the sound can play at.
EndTime - Integer value - End time, in minutes, the sound can play at.
Unk06 - Integer value - Unknown
Unk07 - Integer value - Unknown
Unk08 - Integer value - Unknown
Unk09 - Integer value - Unknown
Unk10 - Integer value - Unknown
Unk11 - Integer value - Unknown
Unk12 - Integer value - Unknown
Unk13 - Integer value - Unknown
ExtParams - Item list - Item list of external parameters


Example:

  <Item type="AmbientRule" ntOffset="16979">
   <Name>ar_construction_grinder</Name>
   <Flags0 value="0xAA001190" />
   <Flags1 value="0x00000000" />
   <Flags2 value="0x00000000" />
   <Position x="0" y="0" z="0" />
   <Flags3 value="0x00000000" />
   <Hash1>construction_grinder</Hash1>
   <Hash2>base</Hash2>
   <Flags4 value="0x00000000" />
   <Flags5 value="0xFFFFFFFF" />
   <Flags6 value="0x00000000" />
   <Unk01 value="1" />
   <InnerRad value="30" />
   <OuterRad value="80" />
   <StartTime value="450" />
   <EndTime value="1176" />
   <Unk06 value="45" />
   <Unk07 value="0" />
   <Unk08 value="0" />
   <Unk09 value="0" />
   <Unk10 value="255" />
   <Unk11 value="255" />
   <Unk12 value="100" />
   <Unk13 value="3" />
   <ExtParams />
  </Item>